des:
Smart Life Britania products help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off your air conditioner
After connecting Alexa to your Smart Life Britania products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Smart Life Britania" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Smart Life Britania account in our "Smart Life Britania" app;
(3). You need to have some Smart Life Britania devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Smart Life Britania" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Smart Britania" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Smart Britania" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Smart Britania", and you'll be navigated to Smart Britania login page;
(9). Input your Smart Life Britania account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on bedroom air conditioner"
